description: A classic Taiwanese drink made with black tea, milk, and tapioca pearls.
Creamy taro-flavored milk tea with chewy tapioca pearls.
Smooth and earthy matcha green tea blended with steamed milk.
Sweet and creamy Thai tea with a hint of spices and boba pearls.
Refreshing honeydew-flavored milk tea with chewy tapioca pearls.
Tropical mango slush topped with boba pearls for a refreshing treat.
Fresh strawberry-infused green tea with sweet boba pearls.
Rich and creamy milk infused with brown sugar syrup and topped with chewy boba pearls.
Fragrant jasmine tea mixed with creamy milk and boba pearls.
Light and refreshing oolong tea infused with peach flavor and boba pearls.
